OL,3,CFood prices see fastest monthly jump
OL,4,Csince April last year
OL,6,FInflation figures show food prices
OL,7,Fwere 1.6% higher in January than a
OL,8,Fyear before, easing from 1.8% in
OL,9,FDecember, according to the BRC-
OL,10,FNielsenIQ Shop Price Index.
OL,12,FFresh food inflation slowed to 0.9%,
OL,13,Fdown from 1.2% in December, while the
OL,14,Fprice of ambient food edged down to
OL,15,F2.5% in January from 2.8%.
OL,17,FWhile overall shop prices fell in
OL,18,FJanuary, the pace of deflation eased
OL,19,Fto 0.7% from December's 1%.
