OL,3,CFood prices see fastest monthly jump
OL,4,Csince April last year
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Extensive January sales was
OL,8,Fgood news for bargain hunters, with
OL,9,Fnon-food products showing significant
OL,10,Fdiscounts, particularly for furniture
OL,11,Fand fashion, but less good news for
OL,12,Fretailers needing to shift excess
OL,13,Fstock.
OL,15,F"This month's figures also showed
OL,16,Fearly signs of what is to come, with
OL,17,Fmonth-on-month food prices rising at
OL,18,Ftheir fastest pace since April last
OL,19,Fyear. Ambient food saw a 1% jump as
OL,20,Fprices spiked for sugary products,
OL,21,Fchocolates and alcohol."
