OL,6,FMs Dickinson added: "Price cuts and
OL,7,Fdeflation may not last much longer as
OL,8,Fretailers will soon feel the full
OL,9,Fimpact of #7 billion of new costs
OL,10,Fannounced at the last Budget.
OL,12,F"Higher employer NICs (national
OL,13,Finsurance contributions), increased
OL,14,Fnational living wage, and a new
OL,15,Fpackaging levy mean that prices are
OL,16,Fexpected to rise across the board."
