OL,3,CFood prices see fastest monthly jump
OL,4,Csince April last year
OL,6,FMike Watkins, head of retailer and
OL,7,Fbusiness insight at NielsenIQ, said:
OL,8,F"Shoppers continue to be unsure about
OL,9,Fspending and many are seeing a
OL,10,Fcontinued squeeze on their household
OL,11,Fincomes.
OL,13,F"So we expect non-food retailers to
OL,14,Fstill promote and food retailers to
OL,15,Fstill offer price cuts over the next
OL,16,Ffew weeks, with shoppers managing
OL,17,Ftheir budgets by shopping smart and
OL,18,Fshopping around for wherever the
OL,19,Fsavings are the most attractive."
